        "bodyEn": "More than 45,000 sq ft of grounds by landscape firm West 8 — tree house, tea pavilion, putting green, stargazing observatory, fire pits, herb garden, outdoor kitchen and a covered dog run. Over an acre of private green space this close to downtown is the one thing rivals can't copy."
