        "bodyZh": "塔顶的 collector 顶层公寓每户独占整层、室内逾 7,400 平方英尺并配私人露台，主卧南向、配双卫与更衣室，并可定制——面向追求整层私密、可塑造空间的顶端买家。",
        "bodyEn": "At the top, full-floor collector penthouses each occupy an entire level — over 7,400 interior square feet with private terraces, south-facing primary suites, dual baths and dressing rooms, and customizable layouts — aimed at the top end of buyers who want whole-floor privacy and a space they can shape."
