        "bodyEn": "Developed by Fisher Brothers, Witkoff and New Valley with Douglas Elliman handling sales, completed in 2018 with immediate occupancy — an established sponsor and a finished, deliverable building remove the timing and completion risk that comes with buying pre-construction."
